{"tid":55874,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"支爆第一波-樂視播放英超訊號中斷","createTime":"2016-12-26T17:32:44.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-26T18:19:14.000Z","uid":19552,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f2fef9f694aa44e3473ce0b51e92adeeb9dbf681","tid":55874,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T17:32:44.000Z","msg":"原來拖緊尾數未找比人cut訊號<br />\n<br />\n又有班港豬比左錢冇野睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"190647a1aae53fc27f6d02e798688ef32811ef78","tid":55874,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T17:36:50.000Z","msg":"傳樂視欠交版權費今晚截英超直播信號　署理CEO否認：無問題<br />\n<br />\n英超賽事正進行得如火如荼，內地有網站卻流傳一條令全港英超迷都震驚的消息：以天價投得英超獨家播映權的樂視欠下版權費，今晚（26日）將被截斷直播信號。樂視體育香港署理首席執行官賴汝正否認有關消息，指今晚觀眾透過樂視收看英超「無問題」；與樂視聯合直播的nowTV亦指，英超播放安排一切如常。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://n2.hk/d/attachments/day_161227/20161227_cd76be8e1733a312d0e6V4MopborI7K6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fn2.hk%2Fd%2Fattachments%2Fday_161227%2F20161227_cd76be8e1733a312d0e6V4MopborI7K6.jpg&h=40f47d89&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"214199b41e26ae9b13a18285897cfbc6fc0f9b1a","tid":55874,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T17:37:28.000Z","msg":"消委會又要忙住幫樂視講好說話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"112e183ffc7015a904adeccd2222f09284428163","tid":55874,"uid":106,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T17:41:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6303177848255961713fc00746092baf7f042f08","tid":55874,"uid":29851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T17:42:55.000Z","msg":"Nice boat <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoj